        <h1>Refund</h1>
At SriCine Cinema, we strive to provide the best movie experience for all our patrons. We understand that sometimes plans change, and we want to make sure you are aware of our refund policy when it comes to ticket bookings.<br>
<br>
<h2>1. Ticket Cancellations and Refunds</h2>
Ticket Cancellation: Tickets once booked through the website or mobile app cannot be canceled. However, under exceptional circumstances, a refund may be requested, subject to approval.<br>
<br>
Refund Eligibility: Refunds may only be issued in cases of:<br>
<br>
Cinemas Closing: If a movie is canceled or rescheduled and you are unable to attend, you are eligible for a full refund.<br>
Technical Issues: If the cinema system malfunctions, resulting in an inability to watch the film, a refund may be processed.<br>
Non-Refundable Tickets: Tickets purchased for special events, premieres, or shows marked as "non-refundable" cannot be refunded once purchased.<br>
<br>
<h2>2. Refund Processing</h2>
Method of Refund: All refunds will be processed to the original payment method used during booking.<br>
Refund Timeframe: Once approved, refunds will be processed within 7-10 business days. Please allow some time for your financial institution to reflect the refund in your account.<br>
<h2>3. How to Request a Refund</h2>
To request a refund, please contact our customer support team at support@sricinecinema.com with the following details:<br>
<br>
Booking Reference Number<br>
Name of the ticket holder<br>
Details of the issue (e.g., movie cancellation, technical issues)<br>
Our customer service team will review your request and contact you with further instructions.<br>
<br>
<h2>4. Refunds for Online Payments</h2>
If you used an online payment method (credit/debit card, net banking, etc.), please ensure that your account details are updated to receive the refund promptly.<br>
<br>
<h2>5. Refunds for Special Circumstances</h2>
<br>Force Majeure Events: In cases where external factors (such as natural disasters, government-imposed lockdowns, etc.) disrupt cinema operations, SriCine Cinema will evaluate the situation and provide a fair solution, including potential refunds or rescheduling of tickets.
<h2>6. General Terms</h2>
Refunds are processed only for eligible tickets. Any claims made outside the specified conditions will not be entertained.<br>
SriCine Cinema reserves the right to modify this refund policy at any time, and any changes will be communicated to customers via the website.<br>
<br>
<h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
If you have any questions or concerns regarding our refund policy, feel free to reach out to us at support@sricinecinema.com or call us at +94 77 1588426.<br>
    
